high_descs: Turn to your right and go to the counter top across from you.
Pick up the head of lettuce to the right of the wine bottle, on the counter top.
Turn to your right and go to the refrigerator, then turn right and go to the sink.
Place the head of lettuce in the sink, turn the water on, rinse the head of lettuce off, turn the water off, and remove the lettuce from the sink.
Turn around and go to the refrigerator across the room.
Place the head of lettuce in the bottom shelf of the refrigerator, to the left of the egg.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean head of lettuce in the refrigerator.

high_descs: Walk forward, then hang a right and walk up to the counter.
Pick up the head of lettuce off of the counter.
Turn right and walk over to the fridge, then turn right and walk up to the sink.
Wash the head of lettuce in the sink and then pick it back up.
Walk over to the black fridge behind you.
Put the clean head of lettuce in the fridge and then close the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean head of lettuce in the fridge.

high_descs: Walk straight then turn right face the counter
Pick up the cabbage on the counter
Turn right then head to the sink
Put the cabbage in the sink then rinse it
Pick up the cabbage then turn left head to the fridge
Open the fridge and put in the cabbage then close the fridge
anns.task_desc: Put the clean cabbage in the fridge
